               "text": "### Images from ESA\n\nThese images are copyright for ESA and allowed to be used according to the license determined by them.\n\nTo visualize all images, use the left and right arrows on the slide below.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 5</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgESA2\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgESA2', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Planck history of Universe. ©ESA – C. Carreau (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('a1a7c478-9061-4160-ba43-301c081733e9'); return false;\"><i>ESA, 09/17/2025</i></a>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">2 / 5</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgESA1\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgESA1', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">View of the Cosmic Microwave Background (CMB) through the ESA Planck mission. ©ESA/Planck Collaboration (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('6006cb3a-9409-4d2a-999c-e4c74249f563'); return false;\"><i>ESA, 09/17/2025</i></a>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">3 / 5</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgUniverseTimeBigBang\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgUniverseTimeBigBang', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">4 / 5</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgWebbDisc\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgWebbDisc', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">5 / 5</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgGaiaStarFormation\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgGaiaStarFormation', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"></div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
